    Extract edge names from pfc object

    pf_edge_names.Rd

    Extract edge names from pfc object

    Usage

    pf_edge_names(x)

    Arguments

    x

    pfc object

    Value

    A character vector of edge names

    Examples

    pf_edge_names(rpfc(100))
